<ul>
<li><strong>Regulatory changes:</strong> Municipal licensing requirements</li></ul>

<ul>
<li><strong>Tourism fluctuations:</strong> Economic or pandemic impacts</li></ul>

<ul>
<li><strong>Higher management complexity:</strong> Requires professional handling</li></ul>

<ul>
<li><strong>Seasonal variance:</strong> Income fluctuates month-to-month</li></ul>

