<ul>
<li>Property is in non-tourist residential areas</li></ul>

<ul>
<li>You want zero involvement in management</li></ul>

<ul>
<li>You prefer stable, predictable monthly income</li></ul>

<ul>
<li>Property type doesn't suit short-term rentals (studio, low floor)</li></ul>

<h2>When Airbnb is Clearly Superior</h2>

<p>Airbnb wins when:</p>

<ul>
<li>Property is in tourist areas (Jonker Walk, coastal, Melaka Raya)</li></ul>

<ul>
<li>You want 2-3x higher returns</li></ul>

<ul>
<li>You want flexibility for personal use</li></ul>

<ul>
<li>Property has features guests seek (views, parking, space)</li></ul>

